{"tid":2028450,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"一個國家究竟有幾廢，先會亂放風又淆底？","createTime":"2020-05-21T22:54:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T12:31:00.000Z","uid":78971,"like":46,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a5e8bc667373e11afdad34907385589c0bc4c256","tid":2028450,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T22:54:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n打又唔打得<br />\n講又冇道理，淨係識發爛渣<br />\n連講數都學人亂咁靠嚇<br />\n<br />\n點知香港人用錢投下神聖一票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n情急之下，「挾香港以嚇美國」都用埋<br />\n而家又話最快半年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n少有國家係攞住自己地方去威脅敵人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n笑死唔笑死<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一國兩制唔係隨意破壞完，<br />\n你一句繼續就回復正常<br />\n<br />\n而家全世界對呢個「一國兩制」好有質疑<br />\n<br />\n好明顯，如果唔做任何改變，<br />\n香港係無可能無條件咁返返去之前"},{"pid":"88f7a6c7ad0a7f615fc69d9c7440732dec1a22d8","tid":2028450,"uid":118125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T23:15:22.000Z","msg":"廢老表示得少少陣痛同衝擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=391821\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D391821&d=ppuFFh6piFuOrul45s7BzfQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=70a63e8a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D391821&h=6c96f0bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=391821</a>"},{"pid":"f29d0442301ff5167a9bd6e5a3244c4015afa909","tid":2028450,"uid":66546,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T23:32:38.000Z",